<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8' ?>
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	xmlns:h="http://java.sun.com/jsf/html"
	xmlns:ui="http://java.sun.com/jsf/facelets"
	xmlns:f="http://java.sun.com/jsf/core"
	xmlns:o="http://omnifaces.org/ui"
	xmlns:of="http://omnifaces.org/functions"
	xmlns:c="http://java.sun.com/jsp/jstl/core">
<h:head>
	<title>#{msg.homeTitle}</title>
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="colorbox.css" target="head" />
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="custom.css" target="head" />
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="fixes.css" target="head" />
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="grid.css" target="head" />
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="reset.css" target="head" />
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="slickmap.css" target="head" />
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="styles.css" target="head" />
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="superfish.css" target="head" />
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="tipTip.css" target="head" />

</h:head>
<h:body styleClass="body">

	<ui:insert name="menu">
		<ui:include src="/resources/templates/menu.xhtml" />
	</ui:insert>

	<ui:insert name="right_pane">
		<ui:include src="/resources/templates/right_pane.xhtml" />
	</ui:insert>
	<ui:insert name="content">
		<h:panelGroup id="wrapper">

			<h:panelGroup class="container_12">
				<div class="main-content">

					<H1>BookDepot Help</H1>
<br /><br /><br />
					<h:link value="Jump to Home" fragment="HomePage" /><br />
					<h:link value="Jump to Cart" fragment="CartPage" /><br />
					<h:link value="Jump to Profile" fragment="ProfilePage" /><br />
					<h:link value="Jump to Search" fragment="SearchPage" /><br />
					<h:link value="Jump to Book" fragment="BookPage" /><br />
					<h:link value="Jump to Checkout" fragment="CheckoutPage" /><br />
					<h:link value="Jump to Invoice" fragment="InvoicePage" /><br />

<br /></div>
					<div id="HomePage">
						
						<H1>HOME</H1>
						<div class="main-content"> 
							<H4>Top panel</H4>
					
							The top panel contains links to different parts of the
							BookDepot web site<br /> Home page, Genres drop down menu,
							shopping cart and login area which allows access to your profile
							when logged in<br /> <br />
							<div>
								<h5>Home</h5>
								 The home button will redirect you to the main home page
								of our web site.<br /> <br />
							</div>
							<div>
								<H5>Genre menu</H5>
								 The genre drop down menu allows for quick access to the
								genre of your choice.<br /> <br />
							</div>
							<div>
								<H5>Shopping cart</H5>
								The cart button will redirect you to your shopping cart
								and allow you to review your selection of books,<br /> modify
								your selection by adding or removing books, proceed with buying
								one or multiple books, as well as <br /> simply reviewing the
								cost of your order. <br /> <br />
							</div>
							<div>
								<H5>Login area</H5>
								The login area will allow you to log into your account
								or create one. <br />
							</div>
						</div> </div>
						<div class="main-content">
							<H4>Right panel</H4>
							
							The right panel contains the search with the criteria you
							would like to search - publisher, author, title or ISBN number.<br />
							It also contains a simplified search by genres that are currently
							available, <br /> a zone for banner ads to generate revenue for
							the web site and a survey available to everybody who visit the
							web site<br /> to voice their opinion. <br /> <br />

							<div>
								<H5>Search</H5>
								The search allows you to find the book you are looking
								for. <br /> Can search by many criteria including publisher,
								title, author and ISBN numbers. <br /> <br /> 
							</div>
							<div>
								<H5>Genre list</H5>
								The genre menu allows for quick access to the genre of
								your choice. <br /> <br /> 
							</div>
							<div>
								<H5>Banner</H5>
								A space for banners to advertise on our site, if you
								would like to be a partner or advertise with us- <br /> please
								contact one of the site managers. <br /> <br /> 
							</div>
							<div>
								<H5>Survey</H5>
								A simple survey to voice your opinions on current site
								matters <br /> Please take the time to choose carefully as you
								will not be able to withdraw your vote. <br />
							</div>

						</div>
						<div class="main-content">
							<H4>Central panel</H4>
							The central area of the web site provides you with three
							randomly picked books from our vast selection,<br /> some news
							and a small section for recently added books to our site.<br /> <br /> 

							<div>
								<H5>Books</H5>
								This area contains three randomly selected books for you
								to read, they're all great!<br /> <br /> 
							</div>
							<div>
								<H5>News</H5>
								 This section contains some book reviews, if you are
								interested click to read the entire article<br /> <br /> 
							</div>
							<div>
								<H5>Recently added</H5>
								 This part contains 4 of the most recently added books to
								our already vast selection!
							</div>

<div class="main-content"> 
						</div>
						<H4>Bottom panel</H4>
			
						The bottom of the page contains the subscription to our
						newsletter and contact details<br /> <br /> 

						<div>
							<H5>Newsletter</H5>
							Subscribe to our newsletter! Simply enter your name and
							email address!<br /> <br /> 
						</div>

						<div>
							<H5>Contact</H5>
							Contact information to get in touch with us!<br /> <br /> 
						</div>
			
				</div>

				<div id="CartPage">
				<H1>CART</H1>
					<div class="main-content">
						<H4>For surrounding panels</H4>
						For the surrounding panels please refer to the appropriate
						sections in
						<h:link value="this section" fragment="HomePage" />
					</div>
					<div class="main-content">
					<H4>Central panel</H4>
					 The central area here contains your shopping cart and allows you to modify it by adding, removing or updating quantities<br /> <br /> 
					<div>
						<H5>Shopping cart</H5>
						Here you will find tools that allow you to remove the book from your order, modify the quantity of each book,<br />
						review the price and see how much it will cost before proceeding to checkout
					</div>
</div>
				</div>




				<div id="ProfilePage">
				<H1>PROFILE</H1>
				<div class="main-content">
					<div>
						<H4>For surrounding panels</H4>
						 For the surrounding panels please refer to the appropriate
						sections in
						<h:link value="this section" fragment="HomePage" />
					</div>
					<br /> 
					<H4>Central panel</H4>
					If you are logged in you will be able to access this page and update your personal information or even change your password <br /> <br /> 

					<div>
						<H5>Profile</H5>
						In this section you will be able to access and change details such as your password,<br />
						location, address and any other personal information which is stored in your profile. <br /> <br /> 
					</div>
</div>
				</div>

			

				<div id="SearchPage">
				<H1>SEARCH</H1>
				<div class="main-content">
					<div>
						<H4>For surrounding panels</H4>
						
						 For the surrounding panels please refer to the appropriate
						sections in
						<h:link value="this section" fragment="HomePage" />
					</div><br /> 
					<H4>Central panel</H4>
					 Upon performing a search you will be presented with a list of books that match your criteria<br /> <br />

					<div>
						<H5>Search results</H5>
						The search results will show the books that matched the search criteria.<br />
						Each result will present the cover for the book, the title and the price at which it is being sold currently.<br /> <br /> 
					</div>
</div>
				</div>

			

				<div id="BookPage">
				<H1>BOOK</H1>
				<div class="main-content">
					<div>
						<H4>For surrounding panels</H4>
						For the surrounding panels please refer to the appropriate
						sections in
						<h:link value="this section" fragment="HomePage" />
					</div><br /> 
					<H4>Central panel</H4>
					The book page will be shown upon selecting a book and will present all the information regarding the selected book<br /> <br /> 

					<div>
						<H5>Selected book</H5>
						This section will present all the information about the book that was chosen and will allow to:<br />
						review information and reviews about the book, choose the quantity and add to cart as well as write reviews about the book.<br /> <br /> 
					</div>
</div>
				</div>

			

				<div id="CheckoutPage">
				<H1>CHECKOUT</H1>
				<div class="main-content">
					<div><br /> 
						<H4>For surrounding panels</H4>
						 For the surrounding panels please refer to the appropriate
						sections in
						<h:link value="this section" fragment="HomePage" />
					</div><br />
					<H4>Central panel</H4>
					This page will allow you to enter payment information and complete your purchase<br /> <br /> 

					<div>
						<H5>Payment</H5>
						This section will allow you to enter payment information for your credit card<br /><br /> 
					</div>
					<div>
						<H5>Details</H5>
						This section will allow you to review your order details and make sure you are getting exactly what you ordered<br /><br /> 
					</div>
</div>
				</div>

	

				<div id="InvoicePage">
				<H1>INVOICE</H1>
				<div class="main-content">
					<div>
						<H4>For surrounding panels</H4>
						 For the surrounding panels please refer to the appropriate
						sections in
						<h:link value="this section" fragment="HomePage" /><br /> 
					</div><br /> 
					<H4>Central panel</H4>
					 This page will allow you to review your invoice after completing the purchase and to send yourself a copy<br /> <br /> 

					<div>
						<H5>Invoice</H5>
						This section will show information regarding the order such as the order id,<br />
						the taxes, total price and date of purchase. <br />
						<br />
						It also allows you to send a copy to yourself
					</div>
</div>
				</div>

			




			</h:panelGroup>
		</h:panelGroup>
	</ui:insert>

	<ui:insert name="footer">
		<ui:include src="/resources/templates/footer.xhtml" />
	</ui:insert>
</h:body>
</html>